  "detailed_description": "<strong><u>Christmas Nightmare is an atmospheric horror game about New Year's Eve.</u></strong><br><br><strong>Plot:</strong> The plot is about just a guy named Connor. All he wants after a hard day at work is to relax on the couch watching his favorite sports show with a bottle of beer.<br>But this evening is special.<br>Evening before New Year.<br><br><strong>Peculiarities:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A short horror game with a total duration of approximately 60 minutes.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The atmosphere of celebration will be replaced by an atmosphere of real horror.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traces in the snow.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fireworks</li></ul>",
